import { Component } from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-root',
  templateUrl: 'app.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['app.component.scss'],
})
export class AppComponent {
  constructor() {}
}
<ion-app>
  <ion-split-pane contentId="main-content">
    <ion-menu contentId="main-content">
      <ion-header>
        <ion-toolbar>
          <ion-title>Menu</ion-title>
        </ion-toolbar>
      </ion-header>
      <ion-content>
        <ion-list>
          <ion-menu-toggle auto-hide="false">
            <ion-item [routerDirection]="'root'" [routerLink]="'/menu-ppal'">
              <ion-icon slot="start" [name]="'home'"></ion-icon>
              <ion-label>
                Menu Principal
              </ion-label>
            </ion-item>
            <ion-item [routerDirection]="'root'" [routerLink]="'/ing-ingr'">
              <ion-icon slot="start" name="pizza-outline"></ion-icon>
              <ion-label>
                Ingresar Ingredientes
              </ion-label>
            </ion-item>
            <ion-item [routerDirection]="'root'" [routerLink]="'/crear-receta'">
              <ion-icon slot="start" name="restaurant-outline"></ion-icon>
              <ion-label>
                Crear Receta
              </ion-label>
            </ion-item>
          </ion-menu-toggle>
        </ion-list>
      </ion-content>
    </ion-menu>
    <ion-router-outlet id=main-content></ion-router-outlet>
  </ion-split-pane>
</ion-app>
